			width: 16vh;
			height: 16vh;
			background: #ff7518;
			left: 1%;
			top: -5vh;
			"
      ></span>
    </div>
    <p class="txtd">
      <a href={exlang + "/gallery"} class="lnk">
        {build_more}
        <br /><br />
